{"tid":2157531,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"拎得lingduck之前得到大家幫手，係時侯撐返蘋果","createTime":"2020-08-15T05:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T01:12:34.000Z","uid":68496,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f34e8e90d3c4cc2b2a04fdb5575e41cec4d636e7","tid":2157531,"uid":68496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:55:12.000Z","msg":"又係我哋拎得lingduck團隊啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自從上次係連登告急後<br />\n<br />\n【告急！本土外賣App就黎撐唔住】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2107622\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2107622</a><br />\n<br />\n得到各位手足支持，情況已經比起5，6月時大為改善。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見到蘋果被打壓，係時候到我地企出黎。大家快d買份蘋果，會見到可愛既黃鴨。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/37EOALW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F37EOALW.png&h=7ed37d45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上一個Post收到好多關於拎得嘅意見，好多人反映「餐廳選擇唔夠！」。所以我地好努力聯絡不同黃店加盟，現時大概增加咗100間餐廳可供選擇，希望手足們可以睇下附近會唔會多咗餐廳可以懲罰；而原有嘅餐廳亦好需要大家嘅繼續支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拎得仲有好多不足，發現任何需要改善嘅，歡迎留言，我地亦都會繼續聯絡黃店加盟，傾獨家自取優惠，務求令大家有更多選擇之餘，仲可以用優惠價幫襯黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n落單連結：<a href=\"https://www.lingduck.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lingduck.com%2F&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8bXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=41328b50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.lingduck.com/</a><br />\n<br />\niOS傳送門：<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/lingduck-%E6%8B%8E%E5%BE%97/id1510386813\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Flingduck-%25E6%258B%258E%25E5%25BE%2597%2Fid1510386813&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8bXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=8d9f324b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/lingduck-%E6%8B%8E%E5%BE%97/id1510386813</a><br />\n<br />\nAndroid 傳送門：<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.lingduck.android\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.lingduck.android&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8bXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=b29ca9dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.lingduck.android</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lingduck.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flingduck.hk%2F&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8bXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=0ca9ed9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lingduck.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\nIG: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/lingduck.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Flingduck.hk%2F&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8bXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=74bbf9ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/lingduck.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n餐廳加盟連結：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/yTEHSKGFqzmdeRAG7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FyTEHSKGFqzmdeRAG7&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8bXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=eb328b27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/yTEHSKGFqzmdeRAG7</a>"},{"pid":"d43d419eefd717dd981cb44758ddbf7e8fc14094","tid":2157531,"uid":219337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:00:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e2609c1a88666a462b81549ea1e42ab0308291","tid":2157531,"uid":68496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:06:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f61874f54c28c089a519d2c08aae1c6f58068ce","tid":2157531,"uid":68496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re